SUMMARY="Nose plugin for integrating JavaScript tests into a Python test suite."

DESCRIPTION="
NoseJS is designed for Python projects that require
JavaScript code for some Web functionality.
It currently has two features:
- Discover and run JavaScript tests alongside Python tests
- Validate JavaScript syntax (check for lint).
"

